{
  "stem": "3165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, I guess my mother was looking for me in the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she opened the door, and she saw me sitting on the porch, and she grabbed me into the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, she told me not to go outside anymore, from here on, by myself, that I always have to stay in the house and be near them, near my parents or my sisters or brothers.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when troubles began with the Gestapos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] Like, do you want me to go in to-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then we heard that Gestapos were coming into different villages and-- taking away Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then one day a neighbor came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she told us-- she told my parents, the next village, the Gestapos are there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're taking away [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're rounding them up and taking them away to the city or the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents took us-- all the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said-- they said, we have to run away now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we ran through the back door through the fields, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] far away from the house into the fields, in high grains to hide.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were staying there, lying down in the grain until it got dark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when darkness came-- evening-- my father said, OK, he's going to go to the house and check and see if the Gestapos were there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, yeah, I spoke to the neighbor, and sure enough they did go through our house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody was in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
